::KitKat::

She snarled at the cat behind the bushes.
"COWARD! MAXIMAL COWARD!"

She turned to face Stringtra and Quickstrike.
"I don't know who you are, but if you are planning on killing this maximal 
scum, please do so.  So far, he really isn't putting up much of a fight.  If 
you wish, I shall leave you to kill him on your own."

She walked back to a tree near the bushes where the cat was and waited.
